likelihood = likelihood_setup.likelihood
F1m, F1v = likelihood.predict_mean_and_var(mu, var)
F2m, F2v = ScalarLikelihood.predict_mean_and_var(likelihood, mu, var)
assert_allclose(F1m, F2m, rtol=likelihood_setup.rtol, atol=likelihood_setup
    .atol)
assert_allclose(F1v, F2v, rtol=likelihood_setup.rtol, atol=likelihood_setup
    .atol)
pytest.mark.parametrize('likelihood_setup',
    filter_analytic_scalar_likelihood('_predict_mean_and_var'))pytest.mark.parametrize('mu, var', [[Datum.Fmu, Datum.Fvar]])
